content: [TextBlock(text='"Boarding my flight back to NYC from Tokyo, the city where I saw blockchain not just as code, but as culture. Japan\'s tech scene is a masterclass in blending tradition with innovation. What I\'ve learned here about community and connection will shape the next phase of my work. Excited to see how this new perspective unfolds back home. #NYCbound"', type='text')]

[TextBlock(text='"Back in the concrete jungle, and the skyline\'s got me thinking: If buildings could vote, would they choose a DAO for governance? 🤔 Time to experiment with some smart contract architecture, literally and figuratively. #NYCbound"', type='text')]
